{"tid":1992221,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［行動post] 星期二晚IFC放工和你唱","createTime":"2020-04-28T04:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T10:45:00.000Z","uid":13193,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5c9224675276b2c9def56065159a69bb3bef7b45","tid":1992221,"uid":13193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WNswLA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWNswLA4.jpg&h=9836f107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#28Apr #中環 #和你唱<br />\n【IFC放工和你唱】<br />\n日期 : <strong>4月28日 (二)</strong><br />\n時間 : <strong>18:30 </strong><br />\n地點 : <strong>IFC</strong><br />\n*留意事項：<br />\n1⃣請帶身分證 , 自備文宣<br />\n2⃣由於疫情和限聚令，活動期間請手足每4人保持1.5米距離<br />\n*前搞手取消 , 本活動與原先搞手無關<br />\nChannel : @Central_2<br />\n<br />\n繼星期日太古城熱身賽，星期二到IFC啦！<br />\n回想上年當日，我同大家喺IFC一齊唱國歌！唱到眼濕濕被Live影到，咁大個仔當住咁多人係大庭廣眾流馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有參與過一定會好感觸，因為香港係大家嘅屋企，見到咁多屋企人咁團結！都咪話唔感動！<br />\n<br />\n今晚要見到大家！經過星期日，相信大家都識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為香港人嘅五一黃金週打氣<br />\n#五一黃金周 #香港人撐黃店<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNxs3p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNxs3p8.jpg&h=4fc48a37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTLBWLa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTLBWLa.jpg&h=d74d67e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"841a0636bfdfbc9df35aaaba39fd6bd8048a0462","tid":1992221,"uid":13193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"好似冇人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7676011bf2f15464329af274338b53f095c11e5b","tid":1992221,"uid":13193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T04:32:04.000Z","msg":"和你唱"},{"pid":"5aee